name: DeleteAssetDeviceRegistration
description: Deletes the resource representing the device connector. All associated REST resources will be deleted. In particular, inventory and operational data associated with this device will be deleted.

name: UpdateAssetDeviceRegistration
description: Updates the resource representing the device connector. For example, this can be used to annotate the device connector resource with user-specified tags.

name: PatchAssetDeviceRegistration
description: Updates the resource representing the device connector. For example, this can be used to annotate the device connector resource with user-specified tags.

name: GetComputeBladeList
description: Get list of blade servers in chassis. Use this for blade servers specifically, not rack servers.

name: GetComputePhysicalSummaryList
description: Get list of all physical servers (compute nodes) in your infrastructure. Use this to retrieve server inventory, hardware details, and server status. This is the primary function for listing servers, server list, getting all servers, listing compute servers, or listing intersight servers. Keywords: servers, compute, physical, inventory, list servers, intersight servers.

name: GetComputeRackUnitList
description: Get list of rack-mounted servers. Use this for rack servers specifically, not blade servers.
